    Services

    Tax

    As a licensed advisory firm, we specialize in the tax area, assisting Polish companies and international entities. We provide support in tax matters, including Polish direct and indirect taxes, international taxation, and tax reviews.

    Accounting

    We offer accounting, reporting, payroll, and advisory services tailored to the individual needs of our clients. We also provide temporary solutions (interim management), which complement or replace the internal financial departments of our clients.

    Transfer Pricing and Valuation

    Our team offers a comprehensive range of transfer pricing and valuation services. In addition to handling documentation required in various countries, we also develop internal pricing policies based on business strategy and solid economic foundations.

    Legal

    Arena Legal is a law firm specializing in a wide range of legal areas. Our services include corporate law (including publicly traded companies), compliance, public procurement, commercial contracts, labor law, management contracts, due diligence, mergers and acquisitions, and regulatory advisory. We operate with passion and professionalism to provide our clients with comprehensive legal services at the highest level.

    Digital

    Our company supports enterprises in improving their business operations and profitability by implementing effective IT solutions. We use the latest technologies that have been tested for efficiency and effectiveness.

    HR and payroll

    The offered HR and payroll services are a key strategy for increasing personnel management efficiency. Outsourcing them to an external company guarantees compliance with legal requirements and the use of best market practices, allowing focus on core business areas.

    Frequently Asked Question

    1. Do you offer support in preparing protective documentation and in negotiations with tax authorities in the event of a tax audit?

    Yes, our company provides comprehensive support in the event of a tax audit, including preparing protective documentation, representing clients before tax authorities, and negotiating to minimize any potential tax consequences.

    2. What are the key steps in mergers and acquisitions transactions from a tax perspective?

    Our team of tax advisors supports clients at every stage of M&A transactions, starting from due diligence, through transaction structuring, to tax optimization of merged companies.

    3. Could you conduct a tax review of our company to identify potential tax risks and optimization opportunities?

    Certainly, our team of specialists will conduct a thorough tax review of your company, identify any potential tax risks, and highlight optimization opportunities, helping you minimize tax risk and maximize tax benefits.

    4. Can you help me identify potential tax incentives for my company considering our industry and business specifics?

    Yes, our team of experts will conduct a detailed analysis of your business and applicable tax regulations to identify all available tax incentives and optimize your tax obligations.

    5. What is your experience in serving international tax clients, especially in the context of complex tax regulations?

    Our firm has extensive experience in serving international tax clients. Our specialists are well-versed in complex tax regulations and international agreements, enabling us to provide high-quality advisory services in the international market.

    6. What are your successes in handling mergers and acquisitions transactions from a tax perspective? Can you provide comprehensive support at every stage of this process?

    Our team of tax advisory specialists has extensive experience in handling mergers and acquisitions transactions from a tax perspective. We offer comprehensive support at every stage of this process, from due diligence, through transaction structuring, to tax optimization of merged companies, ensuring the successful realization of our clients’ business goals.
